Name: sprint_duration
Description: Duration of a sprint in days

Name: team_size
Description: Number of members in a team

Name: feature_estimated_effort
Description: Estimated effort to complete a feature in hours

Name: blocker_severity
Description: Severity level of blockers on a scale from 1 to 5

Name: team_availability
Description: Average availability percentage for team members

Name: sprint_goal_achievement
Description: Completion status of sprint goals as a binary value

Name: feature_priority
Description: Priority level of features on a scale from 1 to 3

Name: stakeholder_influence
Description: Influence level of stakeholders on a scale from 1 to 5
